    • Appointment

      public Appointment(int appId, String title, String description, String type, int custId, String location, LocalDateTime startDateTime, LocalDateTime endDateTime, int contactId, int userId)
      Parameters:
      appId - the ID of the appointment
      title - the title of the appointment
      description - the description for the appointment
      type - the appointment's type
      custId - the ID of the appointment's customer
      location - the location
      startDateTime - the start date/time of the appointment
      endDateTime - the end date/time of the appointment
      contactId - the ID of the contact assigned to the appointment
      userId - the ID of the user who created the appointment
